  <brief_title>Safety and Efficacy of CLBS03 in Adolescents With Recent Onset Type 1 Diabetes (The Sanford Project T-Rex Study)</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Prospective Randomized Placebo-Controlled Double Blind Clinical Trial to Evaluate the Safety and Efficacy of CLBS03 (Autologous Ex Vivo Expanded Polyclonal Regulatory T-cells) in Adolescents With Recent Onset Type 1 Diabetes Mellitus (T1DM)</official_title>
